headline.print_headline: What's in the Gaza Peace Deal?
headline.main: What's in the Gaza Peace Deal?

lead_paragraph: Israel and the Palestinians agreed on Tuesday to an Egyptian-brokered plan to end the fighting in Gaza after 50 days of combat in which more than 2,100 Palestinians, most of them civilians, 64 Israeli soldiers and five civilians in Israel were killed.
